{"tid":867263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★賀！】全球經貿戰︰港中小企難捱！三成進出口商考慮裁員","createTime":"2018-10-18T13:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T04:15:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a6d909a54c34e513588a9a2b16117b0e5d72c4","tid":867263,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:50:54.000Z","msg":"貿易戰影響中小企經營環境，香港生產力促進局調查顯示，進出口貿易及批發等三大行業的營商信心指數，均低於50的盛衰分界線，該界別更有<span style=\"color: red;\">高達三成受訪企業考慮裁員</span>。<br />\n<br />\n當局公布今年第四季的「渣打香港中小企領先營商指數」，反映整體市場的綜合營商指數，由第三季的49.7下跌至43，是兩年以來的低位，其中綜合零售業、製造業及進出口貿易及批發表現最差。<br />\n<br />\n報告顯示，進出口貿易及批發業者對前景最悲觀，近半數受訪企業表示，同時看淡「營業狀況」及「盈利表現」，這兩個指數均達有紀錄以來第二低位，並表示公司的生意額已受貿易戰影響，<span style=\"color: red;\">有84%受影響業者正考慮減少投資，另有30%考慮裁員</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181018/bkn-20181018202541061-1018_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181018%2Fbkn-20181018202541061-1018_00842_001.html&d=r3KAKVFNaHluzyQg9s7QthOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=cd92c152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181018/bkn-20181018202541061-1018_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cd19981d6b765a286af9dd81120aabc9511c9f34","tid":867263,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/133811_1d9fcb4f63a440a77c32deb42756910e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F133811_1d9fcb4f63a440a77c32deb42756910e.png&h=529146e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d197baa56c15c5ed30d7eefa1b1b9ca05dedaf6","tid":867263,"uid":61954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"炒三成咁少？<br />\n係都炒曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6058afc2d82b6e3d6517e5d824a3069a56d776","tid":867263,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike